NAME: Guthling
DEX ENTRY: Hatched from a green egg. These birds seek balance in the world.

NAME: Guthbird
DEX ENTRY: Now a juvenile### the bird flies great horizons in the name of Guthix.

NAME: Guthraptor
DEX ENTRY: Known as a bird symbolizing harmony and balance. If it shows up### all is well.

NAME: Zamling
DEX ENTRY: Hatched from a red egg. These birds align with Zamorak.

NAME: Zambird
DEX ENTRY: Birds who fly over battlefields.They are known for enjoying chaos.

NAME: Zamohawk
DEX ENTRY: During the Third Age these hawks were used by falconers under Zamorak.

NAME: Saraling
DEX ENTRY: Hatched from a blue egg. They possess great wisdom from birth.

NAME: Sarabird
DEX ENTRY: With age these birds gain evermore wisdom of law and order.

NAME: Saraowl
DEX ENTRY: A herald of Saradomin. These owls align themselves to wise individuals who respect law and order above all else.

NAME: Chick
DEX ENTRY: Newly hatched from an egg### these birds will one day be killed for feathers by adventurers.

NAME: Chicken_Normal_Form
DEX ENTRY: Gielinor's finest creature and in great abundance. Their feathers make excellent arrows.

NAME: Dreadfowl
DEX ENTRY: While it is unclear how it is connected to the Evil Chicken### they do share a dreadful magic attack.

NAME: Chicken_Varrock_Form
DEX ENTRY: Hardened from the streets of Varrock### this chicken can often be seen fighting a Stray Dog for scraps of food.

NAME: Chicken_Diving_Form
DEX ENTRY: This chicken adapted to underwater life after its home was sunk to the bottom of the ocean.

NAME: Chicken_Karamja_Form
DEX ENTRY: This chicken stowed away on a ship### and has now adapted to the warmer Karamjan climate.

NAME: Chicken_Death_Form
DEX ENTRY: Serving as the steed of Frank### the fifth member of The Horsemen. This chicken has done nothing worth mentioning.

NAME: Chicken_Bandosian_Form
DEX ENTRY: Initially stolen by goblins for food### this chicken is now a devout follower of the Big High War God.

NAME: Chicken_War_Form
DEX ENTRY: The horse of Frank### the fifth member of the clan### 'The Horsemen'.

NAME: Rooster_Normal_Form
DEX ENTRY: While seemingly unusable due to not laying eggs### they are great for getting up early.

NAME: Ernest
DEX ENTRY: A coward went inside Draynor Manor as a dare. Now his shape reflects his spirit.

NAME: Rooster_Karamja_Form
DEX ENTRY: As the inhabitants of Karamja are up before sunrise to hunt### this rooster has nothing to do. Due to this he's lost the ability to crow at all.

NAME: Oomlie
DEX ENTRY: Strictly found inside the Kharazi Jungle### their meat is used in the renowned 'oomlie wrap'.

NAME: Rooster_Bandosian_Form
DEX ENTRY: Instead of signalling the start of the day### these roosters have been trained to crow as a war cry for the Big High War God Bandos.

NAME: Chicken_Famine_Form
DEX ENTRY: The fusion of 4 different chickens sent to certain death. Its power is that of 4 whole chickens.

NAME: Rooster_Varrock_Form
DEX ENTRY: The sounds of this rooster crowing are drowned out by the constant drone of adventurers coming and going from the Grand Exchange.

NAME: Chicken_Pestilence_Form
DEX ENTRY: The Scientist Avalani sent several chicken into the sky to research the clan citadel. Not many returned.

NAME: Chicken_Lizard_Form
DEX ENTRY: It is unclear whether it is a lizard or a chicken. Nor what came first### the egg or the lizard.

NAME: Chicken_Undead_Form
DEX ENTRY: Chickens who died### but became reanimated. They mainly hail from Morytania.

NAME: Chicken_Mystery_Form
DEX ENTRY: A chicken without any clear purpose or meaning. The real mystery is why it exists.

NAME: EvilChicken
DEX ENTRY: A chicken known to eat its fellow chickens. Bad to the bone. It attacks adventurers on sight.

NAME: Swordchick
DEX ENTRY: With a beak mightier than any others### it faces any opponents on land or sea. One of the Homunculus's greatest creations.

NAME: Newtroost
DEX ENTRY: Pretentious and arrogant. It flexes its muscles and howls in the glory of itself and its creator.

NAME: Calf
DEX ENTRY: Unsteady on their feet### they never stray too far from their herd.

NAME: Cow
DEX ENTRY: While they produce milk### most adventurers prefer their hide to make clothes.

NAME: Super_Cow
DEX ENTRY: When a slayer comes near### the matriarch will challenge it to a battle so epic### only cowhide is left.

NAME: Cow_Dairy_Form
DEX ENTRY: Dairy cows are specialized in producing the highest quality milk and can be milked by any passing adventurers.

NAME: Cow_Undead_Form
DEX ENTRY: A cow who died in the ghastly lands of Morytania. Do not drink its milk.

NAME: Cow_Chocolate_Form
DEX ENTRY: According to several surveys### 80% of players prefer the Chocolate cow over the vanilla or strawberry ones.

NAME: Cow_Strawberry_Form
DEX ENTRY: Strawberry cows come to be by feeding a dairy cow plenty of strawberries throughout its period of growth.

NAME: Cow_Vanilla_Form
DEX ENTRY: It is said that if you shake a vanilla cow enough and use a bucket on it### it will create a milkshake.

NAME: Cow_Harlequin_Form
DEX ENTRY: A cow posessing the rare qualities of its fellow cows. When slaughtered### the pink parts are usually left behind.

NAME: SkeletalOx_Female_Form
DEX ENTRY: An undead bovine who has lost its skin. For some reason### this one is prone to sneezing. How can something sneeze without any lungs..?

NAME: Bull
DEX ENTRY: Angry and impatient### these monsters do not like fashionable people in red.

NAME: Bull_Elder_Form
DEX ENTRY: The apex of bulls. They are capable of knocking players over### and filling their stomachs for a slayer task.

NAME: SkeletalOx_Male_Form
DEX ENTRY: An undead bovine who has lost its skin. They are great companions for teenage witches.

NAME: Trojan_Cow
DEX ENTRY: Fred the farmer collects balls of wool in order to create the ultimate cow. The trojan cow.

NAME: Cow_Plague_Form
DEX ENTRY: The cows of Sophanem and Menaphos were cursed by the Devourer### and are thus slowly awaiting death.

NAME: Minotaur_Normal_Form
DEX ENTRY: Far smarter than regular cows or bulls### they reside in the Stronghold of Security for no apparent reason.

NAME: Minotaur_Rune_Form
DEX ENTRY: Whenever they see humans with horny helmets### they will ruthlessly charge at them for a duel.

NAME: Unicow
DEX ENTRY: An experiment crossing the purity of a unicorn### with the shape of a cow. Its purity it still in question.

NAME: Rat_Normal_Form
DEX ENTRY: While very small### they are sometimes capable of killing kittens.

NAME: Giant_Rat_Normal_Form
DEX ENTRY: Too big for any cat to hunt. These rats lurk about in the wild in search of food.

NAME: Brine_Rat
DEX ENTRY: A rat who lurks in the brine of the sea. They hold on to brine sabres.

NAME: Giant_Rat_Blessed_Form
DEX ENTRY: Iban### son of Zamorak### blessed these beings making them stronger than regular rats.

NAME: Rat_Hell_Form
DEX ENTRY: Demonic rats### they are MALICIOUSLY CRUEL to anyone and TOTALLY EVIL.

NAME: Giant_Rat_Hell_Form
DEX ENTRY: Bigger than before### they are now capable of UNRELENTING MALICIOUSNESS.

NAME: Shell_Rat
DEX ENTRY: A being so BRUTALLY ANTAGONISTIC it could not pass the custom. So it entered a coconut.

NAME: Rat_Crypt_Form
DEX ENTRY: The crypts of Morytania warped these small rats### hardening their skills and aggresion.

NAME: Giant_Rat_Crypt_Form
DEX ENTRY: Despite living in a crypt### this rat is beyond fat. All rats used to look more like this before.

NAME: Warped_Rat
DEX ENTRY: A rat warped by a necromancer. Opening its mind to psychic powers### but losing the sanity.

NAME: Zombie_Rat
DEX ENTRY: Arisen from death### they serve as guards to Melzar the Mad.

NAME: Giant_Rat_Dungeon_Form
DEX ENTRY: Rats adapting to the life in the dungeon. Their scars are from many battles with other rats.

NAME: Rat_King_Form
DEX ENTRY: A rat so deadly it could kill kittens with a single strike. They are known to form rat courts.

NAME: Giant_Rat_King_Form
DEX ENTRY: A king rat who lived to become a giant. Its hedonism and cruelty grew correspondingly.

NAME: Albino_Rat
DEX ENTRY: A rat that has become white and with red eyes. They can not stop themselves from feasting on cheese.

NAME: Angry_Rat
DEX ENTRY: Formed by the anger of Tolna### shaped to a rat. It knows only anger.

NAME: Experiment_2_Form
DEX ENTRY: The experiment of a witch. They fling ogleroots as their weapons.

NAME: Lamb
DEX ENTRY: Woolless and unready for the world. The lamb only hopes to baa with its parents.

NAME: Sheep_White_Form
DEX ENTRY: The favoured race of Guthix. Mostly sheared illegally by adventurers.

NAME: Sheep_Plague_Form
DEX ENTRY: A sheep coloured to pretend there was a plague in Kandarin. This was instigated by the faction of mourners.

NAME: Sheep_Black_Form
DEX ENTRY: Sheep born with black fur are worth less than white ones because their wool can not be coloured.

NAME: Ram_Fluffy_Form
DEX ENTRY: Its horns signals it's ready to fight other males for dominance.

NAME: Ram_Shaggy_Form
DEX ENTRY: Not as easily sheared as sheep### these monsters enjoy striking back at unprepared adventurers.

NAME: Ram_Golden_Form
DEX ENTRY: Golden rams tend to be monopolised by the troll Lalli. But their wool can be used to create enchanted lyres.

NAME: Sheep_Pirate_Form
DEX ENTRY: When a pirate accidentally said he wanted a 'pirate sheep' his crewmates gave him this. It was accepted into the crew.

NAME: Goat_Billy_Form
DEX ENTRY: Known for eating almost anything### these goats are great for controlling grasslands on the mountain.

NAME: Goat_Desert_Form
DEX ENTRY: As they wander the desert near Nardah they sometimes find adventurers killing them for their horns.

NAME: Goat_Mountain_Form
DEX ENTRY: Their hooves are so expertly crafted### they can climb even the steepest mountain. Despite this### they are often used for soup.

NAME: Gorak
DEX ENTRY: Despite being found in another plane of existence### some made it to Gielinor to fight by Zamorak's side during the God Wars.

NAME: Sardine
DEX ENTRY: A small and otherwise weak fish. But rich in nutrients and purines.

NAME: Herring
DEX ENTRY: Not to be confused with red herrings from Sinclair Mansion. These fish live their entire lives in water.

NAME: Trout_Normal_Form
DEX ENTRY: Capable of crossing great lengths of water to mate### these fish can swim an entire day without rest.

NAME: Swordfish
DEX ENTRY: Sporting a sword-like nose### these fish are very territorial over their turf.

NAME: Trout_Leaping_Form
DEX ENTRY: As they are much more agile than regular Trout### these fish are often only caught by those who have received Barbarian training.

NAME: Sturgeon
DEX ENTRY: Its nose is long for territorial fights### as well as a handy tool for examining areas.

NAME: Trout_Tropical_Form
DEX ENTRY: Accustomed to a warmer climate### these fish usually appear in rock pools by the beach during the height of summer.

NAME: Sailfish
DEX ENTRY: Their sail allows them to travel at far greater speed than swordfish### making them exceptional hunters.

NAME: Thallasus
DEX ENTRY: The beast of the sea### it has been known to drown even the biggest ships and seasoned fishermen on the smallest of whims.

NAME: Bass
DEX ENTRY: Often dropped on the ground by adventurers. These fish often feel lonely and neglected.

NAME: Salmon_Normal_Form
DEX ENTRY: When it is time to mate### these fish will climb the Baxtorian Falls### avoiding the whirlpools### to find a mate.

NAME: Shark_Normal_Form
DEX ENTRY: A fish sporting a great number of teeth that can be regrown. Adventurers like to eat these in large numbers cooked.

NAME: Fury_Shark
DEX ENTRY: It is unknown where these shark hail from. Some theorise they can only live inside lava.

NAME: Salmon_Leaping_Form
DEX ENTRY: Scaling the Baxtorian Falls has left these fish significantly more agile and much more difficult to bait.

NAME: Shark_GreatWhite_Form
DEX ENTRY: The most dangerous of all sharks### these fish will lash out and bite anything they find or deem edible.

NAME: Shark_Tiger_Form
DEX ENTRY: A shark only found in the middle of the sea. They sometimes get caught in the fishing trawler### but most expeditions end up a wreck.

NAME: Mackerel
DEX ENTRY: During the reign of Captain Rabid Jack### a man was filled to the brim with mackerels as punishment.

NAME: Catfish
DEX ENTRY: Despite its name### it is not a cat but rather a fish. The whiskers threw marine biologists off.

NAME: Shark_Baron_Form
DEX ENTRY: It is so rare and golden that it is sometimes hung up on the walls of houses. A rare prize for fishermen.

NAME: Tarpon
DEX ENTRY: A vital ingredient for fish oil### hailing from Waiko.

NAME: Seerfish
DEX ENTRY: These fish are apparently distantly related to the mackerel### despite their uppity name.

NAME: DesertSole
DEX ENTRY: Since it is only found in the desert. It hides along the ocean floor camouflaged.

NAME: Sillago
DEX ENTRY: A rare fish from the Arc. It scours the reef hiding from predators and looking for food.

NAME: Wobbegong
DEX ENTRY: Despite its ferocious look it is actually not dangerous to humans### preferring to hunt small fish.

NAME: Karambwanj
DEX ENTRY: A fish that is hard to catch### only catchable in Karamja. It is very poisonous.

NAME: Karambwan
DEX ENTRY: An octopus whose method of being caught was a mystery to mostly anyone but the Tai Bwo Wannai. Nowadays everyone knows about it.

NAME: Whitefish
DEX ENTRY: A rare fish that feeds on slimy eels. They can be crushed and used as bleach to decolour clothes.

NAME: Beltfish
DEX ENTRY: A fish so long it could be used as a belt. Apparently this is how it got its name.

NAME: Manta_Ray
DEX ENTRY: A deep sea fish usually only found through fishing trawlers. They taste delicious but are hard to come by.

NAME: Cod
DEX ENTRY: A fish that often gets the blame for children becoming angry or aggressive to others. It is unknown why.

NAME: Rainbow
DEX ENTRY: As it shines in every colour conceivable### it was almost fished to extinction at one point.

NAME: Shark_Golden_Form
DEX ENTRY: A rare shark with a seemingly kind grin on its face. They are mostly seen in aquariums.

NAME: Pike
DEX ENTRY: A fish known for its green colour. Only about half the pike fished by adventurers actually get cooked.

NAME: Monkfish_Normal_Form
DEX ENTRY: Only found in the Piscatoris fishing colony### they are sought after by sea trolls who fight humans for the land.

NAME: AnglerFish
DEX ENTRY: A fish that captivates its prey with a shining light. As they adore the light### it bites and swallows them whole.

NAME: Giant_Carp
DEX ENTRY: A carp that could single handedly win someone a fishing contest. But it's tricky to bait it.

NAME: Monkfish_Fresh_Form
DEX ENTRY: Not to be confused with regular monkfish that can actually be cooked and eaten.

NAME: Monkfish_Golden_Form
DEX ENTRY: A monkfish so rare### that it's hardly eaten. Most find their way to aquariums in houses.

NAME: GoblinFish
DEX ENTRY: A fish that only lives in the caves of the Dorgeshuun. Its taste is said to be very unique.

NAME: Pet_Fish
DEX ENTRY: Unable to live beyond their fish bowl container. They become quite discontent with their limited life.

NAME: Gilbert
DEX ENTRY: A fish who wanted to see more than the ocean... But ironically needed to see the world through the ocean.

NAME: Cavefish
DEX ENTRY: Living its entire life in underground water### it is unknown if they can even see in light.

NAME: Rocktail
DEX ENTRY: Hard as a rock. Even harder to bite. These fish are tasty treats to most adventurers.

NAME: Eel_Slimy_Form
DEX ENTRY: An eel whose only defensive strategy is to be so slimy it can slip out of any situation.

NAME: Eel_Cave_Form
DEX ENTRY: It prefers the water in caves. It had peace and solitude until the Dorgeshuun realized their existence.

NAME: Eel_Sacred_Form
DEX ENTRY: An eel that used to be worshipped in the past for its spiritual powers. Nowadays they are eaten like any other eel.

NAME: Eel_Lava_Form
DEX ENTRY: This fish can only survive in lava and requires special methods to be caught. One is needed to enter the Heroes' Guild.

NAME: Eel_Infernal_Form
DEX ENTRY: An eel once feared as an eel from Infernus### dimension of demons. No one knows### or cares### if that's true since it tastes delicious.

NAME: Eel_Mottled_Form
DEX ENTRY: Known for their mottled texture### these eels tends to be fished with the aid of falconry.

NAME: Eel_Short_Finned_Form
DEX ENTRY: Everything but appetizing### these eels are known for their many short fins.

NAME: Eel_Salve_Form
DEX ENTRY: For unknown reasons these eels seem to have some lesser holy qualities to them.

NAME: Eel_Dusk_Form
DEX ENTRY: Eels that enjoy lurking in the darkest of waters as to not be caught. When caught### they are anything but pretty.

NAME: Cave_Moray
DEX ENTRY: The biggest of all water-dwelling monsters of Daemonheim. The Cave Moray is a meal in itself for adventurers.

NAME: Vile_Fish
DEX ENTRY: A fish so vile### no one would ever attempt to eat one. Except maybe Thok.

NAME: Piglet
DEX ENTRY: These small things serve no real purpose to farmers but to grow into mud wrestlers.

NAME: Pig
DEX ENTRY: Rumour has it that pigs do have a purpose beyond merely mud wrestling. But the farmer who spread the rumour refused to tell.

NAME: Pigzilla
DEX ENTRY: The apex of all pigs. It's said no pig has ever grown bigger than the Pigzilla.

NAME: Puppy_Pup_Form
DEX ENTRY: A cute little pupper that would die for you. Whenever you leave home### it will stay by your door until you come back.

NAME: Puppy_Mutt_Form
DEX ENTRY: Slightly less adorable than its counterpart### this puppy spends all its free time chewing anything in sight.

NAME: Terrier
DEX ENTRY: In ancient times### these were used for hunting and detective work.

NAME: Sheepdog
DEX ENTRY: Used to guard sheep. These dogs will bark at anyone out of line### or run them down a cliff.

NAME: Dalmatian
DEX ENTRY: It is unknown how many spots a dalmation can truly have. The only thing we know is that some are brown and without any.

NAME: Greyhound
DEX ENTRY: Known for their excellent speed### people use them for gambling in races.

NAME: Bulldog
DEX ENTRY: Ready to fight at any moment. These dogs often get breathing problems.

NAME: Labrador
DEX ENTRY: Genetically engineered to emotionally love everyone. Loves head pats too.

NAME: Corgi
DEX ENTRY: Dogs that faithfully serve their queen### as long as they get lots of treats in the process.

NAME: Terror_Dog
DEX ENTRY: A dog warped by Tarn in order to find the salve stone### he never succeeded.

NAME: Stray_Dog
DEX ENTRY: A mangy mutt who wanders the street### looking for the occasional bone and adventurers to follow.

NAME: Muncher
DEX ENTRY: A skeletal hellhound who served as the lord of Death### Harold's faithful companion.

NAME: Hellpuppy
DEX ENTRY: When a puppy accidentally fell to the infernal dimension### it came back as a hellpuppy.

NAME: Hellhound
DEX ENTRY: A Shakroth type demon from Infernus. They bite really hard if not fed.

NAME: Cerberus
DEX ENTRY: Known for its 3 heads### it's unknown if the heads act as one or if they retain individual personalities.

NAME: Kitten
DEX ENTRY: Small and curious about the world. A kitten will do anything to play with a ball of wool.

NAME: Cat_Normal_Form
DEX ENTRY: Known for their rat hunting prowess### they have become a mainstay in Gielinor.

NAME: Cat_Overgrown_Form
DEX ENTRY: Since it has now grown to full size### it has become too lazy to actively hunt rats. The cat simply can not find the energy.

NAME: Cat_Lazy_Form
DEX ENTRY: When a wily cat does not exercise it becomes a lazy cat. Out of shape and out of motivation. Just like its owner.

NAME: Cat_Wily_Form
DEX ENTRY: A cat trained to peak condition. Ready to strike at any rat it sees. They would fight a giant rat if allowed to.

NAME: Cat_Purple_Form
DEX ENTRY: Cat made purple by the powers of a sweet-tooth witch. It is unknown if there is more to it beyond the colour.

NAME: Cat_Hell_Form
DEX ENTRY: When a cat eats too many hell rats### they become a hellcat. Infused by the hell rats' infernal energy.

NAME: Cat_Post_Form
DEX ENTRY: Letters connect people### and cats connect cat lovers. The postcat is an epitome of them both.

NAME: Cat_Sunken_Form
DEX ENTRY: Sent as an omen to warn the adventurer of a terrible### terrible future. A sunken future. It also removes special effect on command.

NAME: Bob
DEX ENTRY: The reincarnation of Odysseus### the mighty panther who died in a battle versus the dragonkin. Really likes Fish.

NAME: Evil_Bob
DEX ENTRY: An evil tyrant of whom most who have seen rarely survive. He takes slaves in to put them through cruel services like uncooking fish.

NAME: Pet_Rock
DEX ENTRY: Known as the best companion an adventurer could ever have. They will fetch any stick thrown.

NAME: Rock_Polished_Form
DEX ENTRY: Created by betraying a friend and turning them into a polishing rock for the purpose of completing a quest.

NAME: Pillar
DEX ENTRY: The Elder Gods created several Elder Artefacts. The Pillar was not one of them. Despite this### it killed Mother Mallum in one attack.

NAME: Rock_Soup
DEX ENTRY: A troll delicacy made by mixing a pet rock into a soup of cabbage. You can really taste the rock in it.

NAME: Slagilith
DEX ENTRY: Most Slagilith are caused by unknowing adventurers animating the face of a rock. It becomes sentient and will try to kill them.

NAME: Rock_Strange_Form
DEX ENTRY: These rocks are known to sneak into a player's inventory when they are least needed.

NAME: Rock_Golden_Form
DEX ENTRY: These golden rocks are known to sneak into a player's inventory when they are sometimes needed.

NAME: Party_Rock
DEX ENTRY: They dance with the fury of a mighty statue. Having one at a party is sure to raise the roof.

NAME: Strykewyrm_Freezy_Form
DEX ENTRY: The different forms of strykewyrms are well adapted and dangerous. This one is known for being so cold it numbs adventurers hands.

NAME: Strykewyrm_Leafy_Form
DEX ENTRY: Inhabiting the jungles of the Feldip Hills### these strykewrym have adapted to develop a particularly potent poison as a defence mechanism.

NAME: Strykewyrm_Sandy_Form
DEX ENTRY: These monsters burrow under the sands of the Kharidian Desert and burst out the ground to attack unsuspecting victims.

NAME: Strykewyrm_Wildy_Form
DEX ENTRY: A creature of pure fire### this monster originates from the Lava Maze deep in the Wilderness.

NAME: Scorpling
DEX ENTRY: While small### these arachnids pack a real punch if an adventurer gets stung.

NAME: Scorpion_Normal_Form
DEX ENTRY: These scorpions are far bigger than most adventurers.

NAME: Scorpion_Pit_Form
DEX ENTRY: Scorpions### often nesting in pits### looking for scorpionite to eat.

NAME: Scorpion_Poison_Form
DEX ENTRY: The poison they produce is strong enough to kill a Kharidian Sheikah.

NAME: Scorpion_King_Form
DEX ENTRY: Fighting its way to the top### it has become the apex of all scorpions in its group.

NAME: Scorpion_Grave_Form
DEX ENTRY: This scorpion got its name for killing a grave digger who dug near a scorpion pit.

NAME: Scorpion_Corrupted_Form
DEX ENTRY: Scorpion corrupted by the Devourer### granting it power at the loss of its will.

NAME: Scorpion_Reanimated_Form
DEX ENTRY: Unwillingly sent back to the mortal realm### this reanimated being just exists.

NAME: Scorpion_Gauntlet_Crystalline_Form
DEX ENTRY: Uncorrupted### these scorpions find their homes in the Gauntlet.

NAME: Scorpion_Gauntlet_Corrupted_Form
DEX ENTRY: A corrupted crystalline scorpion### now no longer holding a light within it.

NAME: Scorpion_Khazard_Form
DEX ENTRY: General Khazard's pet. It has been trained to fight his prisoners.

NAME: Scorpion_Spirit_Form
DEX ENTRY: In the spirit realm they are known as vicious fighters preying on other spirit inhabitants.

NAME: Scorpia
DEX ENTRY: A vicious and cruel beast ready to kill and eat anything willingly entering its domain.

NAME: Dreadnip
DEX ENTRY: Small and fierce### they will run at any enemy they see trying to eat them

NAME: Peepling
DEX ENTRY: Has a curious eye for everything. Many adventurers have gone mad from their stares.

NAME: Sneakrpeep
DEX ENTRY: Some say they watch adventurers and their every action to learn. Some theorize they gaze into their soul.

NAME: Runtstable
DEX ENTRY: Made by a Gorajo### it lurks the Polymore Dungeon for food.

NAME: Basilisk
DEX ENTRY: With its petrifying gaze### anyone who challenges it without a mirror will be left a garden ornament.

NAME: Baby_Mole
DEX ENTRY: Small and harmless### it will one day grow big enough to destroy any gardeners dream.

NAME: Giant_Mole
DEX ENTRY: A pest to Gardener Wyson. This mole destroys the Falador garden from below.

NAME: Squirrel
DEX ENTRY: Happily jumping around without a care in the world. They often forget where they bury their nuts.

NAME: Ravenling
DEX ENTRY: Hatched from a black egg. They rarely leave their nest on purpose.

NAME: Raven_Normal_Form
DEX ENTRY: Known to pick up anything shiny. If you find a birds nest with a ring in it### it most likely belonged to a raven.

NAME: Raven_Nevermore_Form
DEX ENTRY: Once upon a midnight dreary this ghastly grim and ancient raven can be found wandering from the nightly shore.

NAME: Raven_Spooky_Form
DEX ENTRY: It flies in the night while calling for its ghostly friends. Not many show up.

NAME: Raven_Crystal_Form
DEX ENTRY: Said to be the harbringer of the end### their allegience is to Seren.

NAME: Crow
DEX ENTRY: A flock of crows often lurks around cities looking for food.

NAME: Magpie
DEX ENTRY: It picks up shiny objects from everywhere. But is most known by summoners for its horrible cockney accent.

NAME: Chinchompa_Grey_Form
DEX ENTRY: Capable of running great lengths. All barbers in Misthalin use them as energy.

NAME: Chinchompa_Red_Form
DEX ENTRY: While usually passive### if provoked### they will put their all into exploding as a last resort.

NAME: Chinchompa_Gold_Form
DEX ENTRY: A chinchompa with a golden coloration. They sell for a wealthy prize but do not explode.

NAME: Vultling
DEX ENTRY: Rarely leaving its nest before they can fly### they survive on scraps given by their parents.

NAME: Vulture
DEX ENTRY: Preying mostly on carcasses### they are important to the ecosystem as they remove diseased bodies from the world.

NAME: Pengling
DEX ENTRY: Young and immature### they mature fast as they learn of their oppressors.

NAME: Penguin
DEX ENTRY: Secret agents of the K.G.P on an undercover mission. Easily bribed by fish and cowbells.

NAME: Penguin_Clockwork_Form
DEX ENTRY: Penguin toy made of clockwork. If someone was small enough to fit### they could probably control it from the inside.

NAME: The_Thing
DEX ENTRY: A perfectly normal sheep. In no way is it collecting information about you to use against you.

NAME: Ping
DEX ENTRY: A musician fighting against the K.G.P from the inside.

NAME: Pong
DEX ENTRY: Rebellious in spirit its song invokes glee and glamour in penguins.

NAME: Penguin_McGraw_Form
DEX ENTRY: A penguin wearing a hat to distinguish itself from other penguins similar to it.

NAME: Penguin_Spy_Form
DEX ENTRY: The vanguard of the K.G.P who investigate everything related to humans and their world.

NAME: Penguin_Agent_Form
DEX ENTRY: A agent from the K.G.P fighting endlessly to take over the world.

NAME: Penguin_Disguise_Cactus_Form
DEX ENTRY: Disguising themselves as cactus these spies roam the desert.

NAME: Penguin_Disguise_Rock_Form
DEX ENTRY: Next to a pet rock it's hard to tell which one might pick up a stick.

NAME: Penguin_Disguise_Bush_Form
DEX ENTRY: In forests they stand perfectly still to not be spotted by anyone or anything.

NAME: Penguin_Disguise_Box_Form
DEX ENTRY: Hiding in boxes allows them to check urban areas for intelligence.

NAME: ExExParrot
DEX ENTRY: Used to be a real parrot but they are no more### it's gone### and it longs for the fjords.

NAME: Broav
DEX ENTRY: With a great sense of smell### they are able to find anything from truffles to secret trapdoors.

NAME: Tooths
DEX ENTRY: A creature created by the magic of the Tooth Fairy. They turn rotten if they eat chocolate.

NAME: Rune_Guardian
DEX ENTRY: Created by rune crafting wizards### this automation is easily influenced by runic energy.

NAME: Gnomey
DEX ENTRY: Given to winners of the Golden Gnome awards. Most being for pity or lack of competition.

NAME: Sparkles

DEX ENTRY: Sent by The Devourer### Zebak kills any intruder to its tomb.

DEX ENTRY: The rarest of all Zygomites. It's said to be so rare hardly anyone has seen it in decades.

DEX ENTRY: A creature that lives between realms. Its face confuses all.

NAME: Airut

NAME: Scurrius_Magic_Form
DEX ENTRY: Despite being a much smaller part of the whole rat king### some believe Scurrius' mage head ultimately controls it.

DEX ENTRY: This impling can't be caught### instead it tells adventurers of its magical home plane### Puro-Puro.

DEX ENTRY: These implings pick up necrotic energy to store### but adventurers always steal it.

DEX ENTRY: The tail on this jerboa looks like a small flame. When it runs### the flame flickers.

NAME: Antelope_Moonlight_Form
DEX ENTRY: This antelope is rarely seen at daytime. In moonshine### it walks proudly.

DEX ENTRY: Able to befriend anything it meets### the capybara exists to be the best.

NAME: Capybara_Orange
DEX ENTRY: The orange on its head stands as proof of its superiority.

NAME: Entling
DEX ENTRY: The joyful spawn of an ent### these appear randomly to ask adventurers to prune them. They stun anyone who does not prune them properly.

DEX ENTRY: If pigs could fly### they would be happy too. Piggles is happy you gave money to Jagex to get him.

DEX ENTRY: When a Flesh Spoiler sheds itself these are what remain. Creating more Flesh Spoilers.

NAME: Tome_of_Strength
DEX ENTRY: An ancient tome of melee secrets summoned by the only known librarimancer in Gielinor.

NAME: Tome_of_Ranged
DEX ENTRY: This ancient tome contains ranged combat secrets### and is part of Lexicus' Almanac Army.

DEX ENTRY: An ancient tome of arcane secrets. It has been enchanted by Lexicus to attack anyone who dares cross him.

NAME: Dromomastyx

NAME: Spinomastyx
DEX ENTRY: Hunters who gathers their hide can create good armour from this beast. But will never use it since it uses up their binds.

NAME: Gallimastyx
DEX ENTRY: Some argue that their brain is really small. Most people who arent mastyxes agree.

NAME: Stegomastyx
DEX ENTRY: To efficiently catch a mastyx### it is best to set up a guillotine and wait for it to curiocly poke its head in.

NAME: Jelly_Alternate_Form

NAME: Jelly_Vitreous_Form

NAME: Jelly_Warped_Vitreous_Form

NAME: Moth_Moonlight_Form

NAME: Spirit_Ranger

NAME: Esswraith

DEX ENTRY: Some of these mages can summon reborn warriors to their aid.

NAME: Cockatrice_OSRS_Form

DEX ENTRY: Large energies and memories from the shattered world caused this being to exist.

NAME: Yak_Lumber_Form

NAME: Har_Aken
DEX ENTRY: An ugly piece of shit Jagex thought could replace Jad. It cant because it is UGLY.

NAME: Har_Aken_Tentacle
DEX ENTRY: That goes for you too you tentacle fuck.

NAME: Jadinko_Ferocious

NAME: Jadinko_Draconic
DEX ENTRY: Embodying all aspects of a dragon this Jadinko is everything a dragon is except being a dragon

NAME: Flesh_Crawler

NAME: Zygomite_OSRS

NAME: Rockslug_RSHD

NAME: Rockslug_OSRS

NAME: Snail_Thorny

NAME: Snail_Bruise_OSRS

NAME: Mother_Mallum
DEX ENTRY: Trapped for ages due to her power. Mother Mallum is a force feared by the temple knights.
